content.rendered:
Directed by Omung Kumar.

Written by Anirudh Chawla. Anirudh Chawla. Harsh Limbachiyaa. Vivek Oberoi. Vivek Oberoi. Sandeep Singh.

Cast Vivek Oberoi(Narendra Modi). Manoj Joshi(Amit Shah). Darshan Kumaar(Television Reporter). Anjan Srivastav(Atal Bihari Vajpayee). Barkha Bisht(Jashodaben). Rajendra Gupta(Damodardas Modi). Zarina Wahab(Hiraben Modi). Suresh Oberoi(Baba) . Babita Anant(Mamta Banarji). Jay Bhatt(Mahesh). Bhavik Bhojak(Arjun Patel).Bsinngh. Navneet Gairola(OSD to PM, no name). Sheila Gore(Sonia Gandhi). Imran Hasnee(Zafar). Boman Irani(Ratan Tata). Dilipsinh Jhala(Sr Politician).Yatin Karyekar. Tareeq Ahmed Khan(Azhar). Prashant Narayanan(Businessman). Jimesh Patel(Raju). Tushar Sadhu(Gupta). Raj Saluja(Joshi (as Akshat R Saluja)). Satish Sharma(Satish Sharma).Rajeev Vashishth. Naresh Vohra(Dr. Murli Manohar Joshi)

Languages Hindi. Tamil.

Producers Abhishek Ankur. Ayush Bellore. Tosif Kazi. Akib Khan. Acharya Manish. Zafar Mehdi. Suresh Oberoi. Anand Pandit. Sandeep Singh.

Production Legend Global Studi. Vikrant Studi.
